TopicTitle: Kerbal Space Program Theme for Note Blocks

Articles.Content:
Hello everyone!

It's been ages since I last did a fan thing so here's a new one!

Because I have a love for Kerbal Space Program and Minecraft, I made this Note Block version of the KSP Theme. It's far from amazing but its okayish.

Hope you enjoy!

Direct Soundcloud link: https://soundcloud.com/therandomworldofpcgeek/kerbal-space-program-theme-for-note-blocks

Thanks for listening

Catch you later!

-PCGeek
